import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    data['total_casualties'] = data['wounds'] + data['other'] + data['disease']

    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='total_casualties', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the trend of casualties over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Total Casualties')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(['Total Casualties'])

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]

    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='wounds', bins=20, color='blue', kde=True)
    plt.axvline(data['wounds'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['wounds'].median():.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Number of Casualties due to Wounds')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of casualties due to wounds?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
